## Priority: Critical

`@event` handlers are rejected on component tags. Only native HTML elements accept them. This blocks parent-child event communication for components without `defineEmits`.

## Scope

- Allow `@event` on component elements
- Forward as emit call or native event on component root
- Validate against component's declared emits when available

## Example

```html
<MyButton @click='handleClick' @custom-event='onCustom' />
```